                      <p
                        style="
                          box-sizing: border-box;
                          color: #74787e;
                          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                          font-size: 16px;
                          line-height: 1.5em;
                          margin-top: 0;
                        "
                        align="left"
                      >
                        Thanks for trying [Product Name]. We’re thrilled to have you on board.
                      </p>
                      <p
