                        © 2021 [Product Name]. All rights reserved.
                      </p>
                      <p
                        class="sub align-center"
                        style="
                          box-sizing: border-box;
                          color: #bbbfc3;
                          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                          font-size: 12px;
                          line-height: 1.5em;
                          margin-top: 0;
                        "
                        align="center"
                      >
                        [Company Name, LLC]
                        <br />1234 Street Rd. <br />Suite 1234
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
